tr.td: DescriptionFlag of the United Arab Republic (1958–1971).svg

td.div: English: Flag of Egypt (1958-1971) and flag of Syria (1958-1961) in the United Arab Republic. It also became the official flag of Syria since 1980.

This file was derived from: Flag of Syria.svg
This vector image includes elements that have been taken or adapted from this file: Flag of Syria.svg.
